document_data.name: League of Basketmakers & Wickerworkers Storage
document_data.aliases:
Warehouse of the League of Basketmakers & Wickerworkers
Warehouse of the League
document_data.mainbody: '''League of Basketmakers & Wickerworkers Storage''' also known simply as the '''Warehouse of the League''', was a warehouse in [[Waterdeep]] that was owned by the [[Guilds of Waterdeep|Waterdhavian guild]] of the [[League of Basketmakers & Wickerworkers|same name]].
document_data.Location: This warehouse was located in the [[Waterdeep/Trades Ward|Trades Ward]] of [[Waterdeep]].
